data.description: This 80 acre property has it all including pasture for all your animals, hunting ground, 3 ponds, creek, barn, hobby building, over sized 2 car detached garage with shop area and an additional shed.  Inviting front deck that leads to the beautiful 4 bedroom, 1 bath home with many updates inside and out including roof, siding, c/h/a, plumbing, breaker box, lateral lines, stove and dishwasher.  In the summer months you will enjoy the above ground pool just outside your back door.  Call today for additional information and to schedule your appointment to view this must see property.
